data.description: **Huge Price Reduction** Don't miss this opportunity for a fantastic deal at the end of the year when rates just went down!!! Welcome to 13927 Hudson Way, a stunning single-family residence in Thornton, CO. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, this home offers a spacious and versatile floorplan to accommodate a variety of lifestyles. The main level features a flexible space with multiple living areas and a convenient main-level bedroom that is also a great office space. Upstairs you'll find a huge primary suite with 5-piece luxury bathroom, a functional loft area that would make a great playroom or home office, 2 secondary bedrooms, and a large hall bathroom with double vanity. You'll love the spacious floorplan with the high ceilings and abundant natural light streaming through the numerous windows throughout the home. Additionally, the fully finished basement with bathroom provides a multipurpose area for family gatherings, additional sleeping quarters or guest space, as well as office potential. So many options! This property, nestled in a desirable neighborhood, promises a great location with easy access to amenities and conveniences. The surrounding area is known for its community appeal, offering a harmonious blend of comfort and accessibility. The residence also presents a beautifully landscaped backyard, adding aesthetic charm and a private oasis for outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss this one!
